rows.label: qst700106_msg0001
rows.name:
You must have been scared. I'll
see you home, so don't worry.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0102
rows.name: Just hold on a little longer.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0201
rows.name:
Are you injured at all?
You'll be home soon.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0302
rows.name:
Let's take a safe road
back. No need to worry.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0402
rows.name:
Come on, stop staring off
into space. Let's go home.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0501
rows.name:
You must have been frightened.
You endured well.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0602
rows.name:
...Can you walk? Let's take
it slow on the way back.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0701
rows.name:
...You don't seem to be
hurt anywhere, do you?

rows.label: qst700106_msg0702
rows.name:
Let us go home, to the
one who waits for you.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0801
rows.name:
...Your breathing is fast. Calm
down, and steady your breath.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0802
rows.name: ...Yes, that's it. Come, shall we go?
